Bootstrap:-
------------
Bootstrap is a collection of class selectors.which are available in external css.
Bootstrap internally used jquery library.
Bootstrap is used to make responsive webpages.
Bootatrap provide the look an feel of webpages.

some libraries are used in bootstrap:-
-------------------------------------
bootstrap.min.css(external css)
font-awesome.min,css(external css)
hover.min.css(external css)

jquery.min.js
bootstrap,min.js

Bootstrap 3,Bootstrap 4;

Note:
------
Height is not allowed in bootstrap.
min-height are used in bs.
width are not allowed in bs.
float are not allowed in bs.

Some classes of Bootstrap:-
===========================
Text tag classes in bs:-
-----------------------
text text-success
text text-warning
text text-danger
text text-onfor
text text-uppercase
text text-lowercase
text text-center
text text-default......etc;

image tag classess of bs:-
--------------------------
img img-responsive
img img-circle
img img-thumbnail
img img-rounded

Grid classes of bs:-
---------------------
col-xl-12(extra large devices)
col-lg-12(large devices)
col-md-12(medium devices)
col-xs-12(extra small devices)
col-sm-12(small devices)

Section class:-
---------------
panel panel-heading
panel panel-body

Table classes :-
----------------
table table-responsive
table table-display
table table-sttrped etc.

Icon classes:-
--------------
fa fa-facebook-square
fa fa-facebook
fa fa-google
fa fa-whatsapp
fa fa-twitter
fa fa-globe
fa fa-phone
fa fa-trash
fa fa-envelope............etc.
button classes:-
----------------
btn btn-success
btn btn-danger
btn btn-info
btn btn-warning
btn btn-default
btn btn-lg

Form-control class used in form controls.
hover classes in bs:-
---------------------
hvr hvr-bob
hvr hvr-pulse
hvr hvr-push
hvr hvr-pop............etc;